        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "What is the value of the discriminant for $3x^2 - 2x + 1 = 0$?",
        "options": ["$-8$", "$8$", "$-4$", "$4$"],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "The discriminant is $\\Delta = b^2 - 4ac = (-2)^2 - 4(3)(1) = 4 - 12 = -8$."
